profile:
CMS Cleaning believes in giving our customers the best possible service we can. 
Our team is made up of highly experienced professionals and have served large department stores across Canada since the days of Eaton’s.
We pride ourselves in having 100% customer satisfaction.
If it needs to be cleaned, we can clean it. If it needs to be fixed we can fix it. If it needs to be put together we can do that too.
We are your one stop shop for most everything that has to do with your home. 
We are pleased to be affiliated with a company specializing in post-disaster response. 
Residential and Commercial
Our post-disaster cleanup emergency services are open 24/7 and will help you quickly get rid of the mess and smell caused by fire, smoke and water. A thorough cleaning on all indoor and outdoor surfaces will be performed as well as an evaluation report to be provided upon request. IICRC certified
